id=update_blocker
name=Update Blocker
version=v1.3
versionCode=4
author=RAFSuNX
description=Blocks Android OTA updates at the root level on Pixel. Nulls out /system/bin/update_engine and disables the Factory OTA app. Does not touch GMS/GSF. Requires the OverlayFS MetaModule (meta-overlayfs). Use the Action button to reset update_engine and clear OTA cache.
